Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_inb_chn3

USBN_DMA0_INB_CHN3 = USBN's Inbound DMA for USB0 Channel3

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 writes to L2C via Channel3. Writing of this register sets the base address.
